'''皇家亨利賽艇日'''（{{lang-en|Henley Royal Regatta}}）是每年初夏在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[泰晤士河畔亨利|泰晤士河畔亨利]]的[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]河面上舉辦的賽艇活動，開始於1839年3月26日。皇家亨利賽艇日於每年7月第一個週末（禮拜三至禮拜日）舉行，在1英里長的河面上競速<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hrr.co.uk/history-organisation/the-course/|title=Henley Royal Regatta - History and organisation - The Course|accessdate=2011-06-04|archive-date=2011-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614080429/http://www.hrr.co.uk/history-organisation/the-course/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該活動是英國社交季節重要部分之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.debretts.com/social-season/the-traditional-season.aspx|title=Debretts - the traditional season|accessdate=2011-06-04|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717184937/http://www.debretts.com/social-season/the-traditional-season.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，對參加人員的著裝也有嚴格要求<ref>http://www.whatbesttowear.com/events/henley-royal-regatta/what-to-wear-to-the-henley-royal-regatta/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.whatbesttowear.com/events/henley-royal-regatta/what-to-wear-to-the-henley-royal-regatta/ |date=20110113072329 }} | What to wear to Henley Royal Regatta</ref>。
